quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,53,"Ivyo vyose nukubera yuko Imana idahindura imigisha yahaye abantu bayo naho bokwihindurira kubwabo mubiri mumitima yabo, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo yumva kandi niyo ibifitiye ubumenyi"
  8,54,"Ni nk’abantu bokwa Fir’auni hamwe n’abamyeho imbere yabo, bahakanye amajambo y’Imana matagatifu, kuri ivyo twarabahoneje kubera ibicumuro vyabo hamwe n’ukwibiza abantu bokwa Fir’auni mukiyaga nabose bari mu bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  8,55,"Ibikoko bibi cane imbere y’Imana, nibarya bahakana amajambo y’Imana y’ukuri, nabo ntibazo kwemera nagatoyi"
  8,56,Mubo mwahanye indagano hanyuma bakiyonkora kurizo umwanya uwariwo wose kandi badatinya
  8,57,Rero ubasanze kurugamba nubirukane abari inyuma yabo kugira ngo bikebuke
  8,58,"Niwatinya muri abo bantu biyonjorora, nubasubize ayo masezerano yabo kubungane bwayo, n’Imana ntikunda abiyonjorora"
  8,59,"Canke bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri ntibibaze yuko bamaze gutera intambwe iri imbere, oya! Nibamenye yuko batazotsinda Imana"
  8,60,"Rero nimubitegurire n’ubushobozi mufise hamwe n’amafarasi yaboshwe kandi yateguwe neza, kugira ngo mubatere ubwoba abo bansi b’Imana hamwe n’abansi banyu, hamwe nabatari abo mutazi mwebwe, n’Imana irabazi n’ivyo muzotanga munzira y’Imana muzo bisubizwa bikwiye vyose, kandi ntimuzo hemukirwa"
  8,61,"Nibatumbera munzira y’amahoro nawewe nuyitumbere, kandi wizere Imana yawe kuko niyo yumva kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije"